    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/251d0a39f1c5682233c5118f89194f2d.poster.avif?t=1771430066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/251d0a39f1c5682233c5118f89194f2d.webm?t=1771430066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/251d0a39f1c5682233c5118f89194f2d.mp4?t=1771430066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新体验的连招式 RPG 游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Signy &amp; Mino: Against All Gods》带来一种前所未有的回合制连段玩法，让你在深思熟虑之中打出夸张爆表的连击。站位至关重要：巧妙规划你强力攻击的方向，让目标在被击飞的过程中撞上路径上的其他敌人。把你的目标击飞到空中，对其进行凌空连击，然后将其重重地砸进地里。召唤米诺把被埋进地里的敌人挖出来继续连击，或者牺牲生命值突破极限，直接冲向下一个目标。最后以全画面范围的终结技收尾，把所有被卷入其中的敌人彻底粉碎。而这只是众多连招组合中的其中一种——绝大多数招式在正确时机都能无缝衔接，尽情发挥你的创造力吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/2b87315bcbb8873d6d5b666aa1d440d3.poster.avif?t=1771430066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/2b87315bcbb8873d6d5b666aa1d440d3.webm?t=1771430066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/2b87315bcbb8873d6d5b666aa1d440d3.mp4?t=1771430066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >禁锢之界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >山岳研究中心发生灾难后，各地区之间的交通被全面封锁。踏上旅途，穿越郁郁葱葱的森林，登上神奇的岛屿，探索隐秘的神殿，甚至深入研究中心内部，一步步揭开导致当下局势的连锁黑暗真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/5cb19f0a833ab68c34f6004b34513119.poster.avif?t=1771430066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/5cb19f0a833ab68c34f6004b34513119.webm?t=1771430066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379160/extras/5cb19f0a833ab68c34f6004b34513119.mp4?t=1771430066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >诸神纷争</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场火山喷发掩盖了真正可怕的真相：一位怀恨在心的山之神即将重生。与堕落的神祇和沉寂已久的战士们结成同盟，你将肩负起唯一能够对抗这位不灭之敌的使命。</p>",
